extendedInfo.description: Celebrity Trivia quiz will test you on the biggest stars of today's pop culture.Celebrity Trivia quiz game will test your knowledge of today's biggest stars of movie, music, TV, and pop culture celebrities. If you enjoy reading Entertainment Weekly, Us Magazine, People Magazine, or any celebrity-focused magazine, you'll have fun with this game.Questions include celebrities such as:Heidi Klum, Katy Perry, Courtney Cox, Jim Carrey, Owen Wilson, Britney Spears, Dakota Fanning, Betty White, Natalie Portman, Cory Monteith, Daniel Craig, Megan Fox, Tyra Banks, Scarlett Johansson, Shakira, Leonardo DiCaprio, Joan Rivers, George Clooney, Tom Hanks, Joan Collins, Niki Minaj, Lady GaGa, Jay-Z, Prince William, Tina Fey, Carrie Underwood, Taylor Swift, Gwyneth Paltrow, Johnny Depp, Brad Pitt, Tom Cruise, Hugh Hefner, Miley Cyrus, Justin Bieber, Jonas Brothers, Justin Timberlake, Chelsea Handler, Piers Morgan, Eva Longoria, Reese Witherspoon, Kate Hudson, Nicole Richie, Paris Hilton, Jennifer Aniston, Oprah Winfrey, Usher, Elton John, Eminem, Sting, 50 Cent, Pink, Orlando Bloom, Kelly Clarkson, Adam Lambert, Neil Patrick Harris, Charlie Sheen, Jon Bon Jovi, Celine Dion, Beyonce, Gisele Bundchen, Alex Rodriguez, Paul McCartney, Kevin Costner, Selena Gomez, Kristin Stewart, Drew Barrymore, Nicole Kidman, Seth Rogan, Christina Aguilera, Rihanna, Chris Daughtry, Kate Moss, Michael Jackson, Jessica Simpson, Angelina Joli, Halle Berry, Heidi Montag, Kelly Ripa, Michael Douglas, and Al Pacino.
